    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 备好与Bubbits一起全新体验经典的泡泡射击游戏类型吧！ <strong>现在就发布心愿单</strong> ，今天就加入泡泡射击革命吧！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238070/extras/4bf2ee2d0d5a7a71f3a64be69060cb16.poster.avif?t=1758734460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238070/extras/4bf2ee2d0d5a7a71f3a64be69060cb16.webm?t=1758734460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >所有游戏模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在激烈的2-4人对战模式下，在25人的大型在线大逃杀比赛中与朋友们正面交锋。在每日挑战中挑战世界，或在单人模式中拥抱永恒的经典泡泡射击游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238070/extras/1246df94ac2e766af7020285fc64db7c.poster.avif?t=1758734460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238070/extras/1246df94ac2e766af7020285fc64db7c.webm?t=1758734460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有趣的能量提升&amp;疯狂战斗活动</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放改变游戏规则的能量，并适应改变游戏规则的动态匹配事件。攀登排行榜，展示你的泡泡爆破技能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238070/extras/bb0bba5ec3434d306b875ba86697ea7b.poster.avif?t=1758734460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238070/extras/bb0bba5ec3434d306b875ba86697ea7b.webm?t=1758734460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238070/extras/54c15e9c58ed2f30f14d3684d5368340.poster.avif?t=1758734460\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238070/extras/54c15e9c58ed2f30f14d3684d5368340.webm?t=1758734460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论您是随意玩游戏还是参加Bubbits Royale决赛，都可以发挥您的个人天赋，让每一场胜利都成为您自己的胜利。使用独特的角色定制您的Bubbits体验，调整您的游乐场的外观，如果您进入皇家决赛，请带上您的凹槽。在专用服务器上享受无滞后的在线战斗，您的技能和快速反应真正决定您的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >立即加入</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将Bubbits添加到您的心愿单，为千载难逢的泡泡大战做好准备！无论您是来这里进行大规模的多人游戏还是单人游戏， Bubbits都可以提供不间断的动作，易于拾取，但无法放下！</p>",
